Class ReloadingX509TrustManager

java.lang.Object
javax.net.ssl.X509ExtendedTrustManager
org.infinispan.commons.util.ReloadingX509TrustManager
All Implemented Interfaces:
Closeable, AutoCloseable, TrustManager, X509TrustManager
public class ReloadingX509TrustManager extends X509ExtendedTrustManager implements Closeable
A X509ExtendedTrustManager which uses a @FileWatcher to check for changes.
